<head2>(Using the Tool Palette\paint_tools)

<p>
The tool palette offers a variety of art tools and basic shapes.  
<p>The
shapes on the tool palette let you compose pictures quickly and easily.
<p>
When you first start Paint, the Paintbrush is highlighted,
indicating that it is the current default.  Only one tool on the tool 
palette is
active at a time and that tool remains active until you make another 
selection.

<p>
To choose another tool:

<list>(numbered)

<le>Click MB1 on the tool you want to use.

<le>Position the pointer into the drawing window and click MB1. 

<p>
The new tool is now active in the window. 
<endlist>
<P>
