<head2>(Moving Images\paint_moving)
<p>
You can move an image from one location in the Paint window to another.  
<p>
To
move an image:

<list>(numbered)

<le>Select the image.

<le>Press MB1 inside the selected area and drag the image to
the desired location.
<le>Release MB1.
<endlist>
<p>                                                           
To cancel the selection, click on another part of the window or 
select another tool. 



<P>
