<head2>(Sizing the Canvas\paint_sizing_canvas) 
<p> 
The default Paint window shows only a portion of the canvas.  
<p>
The area of the canvas, with the display window enclosed, appears at the 
bottom of the tool palette as a box within a box.

<p>
Use these boxes to display different areas of the canvas quickly.
Click anywhere 
in the boxed area; the canvas display moves accordingly.
<p>
Alternatively, you can use the horizontal and vertical scroll bars to 
navigate the canvas.

<P>
