<head2>(Saving a Picture\paint_saving)
<p>
You can save both newly created pictures or pictures that you are
revising. 
<p> 
To save a new picture.

<list>(numbered)
<le>Choose the Save As... menu item from the File menu. 
A dialog box appears.

<le>Type a file name using the format filename.img.


<le>Click on OK.  
<endlist>
<p>
To save a revised picture that already has a file name, choose 
Save from the File menu. Paint saves the new version of
your picture.



<P>
