<head2>(Printing a Picture\paint_printing)
<p>
To print a picture, choose either the Print or Print... menu item
from the File menu.  
<p>
The Print menu item sends the picture to the default printer.

<p>  
The Print... menu item displays the Print dialog box and sends the picture 
to the printer you specify.
   
<p>
Paint supports output to both PostScript and sixel printers. 
When printing on an LA50 printer, set an aspect ratio of 2:1.  All other
printers have a 1:1 ratio.


         
<P>
