<head2>(Viewing Pictures with CDA Viewer\cda_view)
<p>
With the CDA Viewer, you can view pictures you create with Paint.
<p>   
 The CDA Viewer lets you look at Compound Document
 Architecture (CDA) files on your screen. The default file 
 format for the CDA Viewer is Digital Document Interchange
 Format (DDIF). 
<p>
 DDIF is a
 standard format for the storage and interchange of
 compound documents. Compound documents contain multiple
 elements, for example, text and graphics.

<P>
