<head3>(Open...\file_open)
<p>
To open a new or existing file, choose Open... from the File menu.
<p>

The Open Picture dialog box appears, which displays a list of your 
directories and files.
<p>
To open an existing file:
<list>(numbered)
<le>In the Directories list box, double click on the directory where your 
file is located.
<le>In the Files list box, double click on the graphics file you want to 
open.
<le>Click on OK.
<endlist>
<p>
To open a new file:
<list>(numbered)
<le>In the Directories list box, double click on the directory where you
want the file to reside.
<le>Click on the Selection entry box.  Enter the new file name with an img 
file type.  For example, picture.img.
<le>Click on OK.
<endlist>

<P>
