<head3>(Include...\file_include)
<p>

The Include... menu item allows you to copy another image file from your 
directory into your current Paint
window, providing the image file is not larger than the canvas.
<p>
To copy an image file from your directory to your window:
<list>(numbered)
<le>Choose Include... from the Edit menu.  The Include dialog box appears.
<le>In the Directories list box, double click on the directory where the
image file is located.
<le>In the Selection entry box, enter the name of the image file you want
to copy to your window.
<le>Click on OK.  The image file is copied to your window.
<endlist>
   

<P>
