<p>
The Undo menu item lets you erase all or portions of the picture.
<p>
Choose Undo to erase all moves made under
your current tool selection.
<p>
Note that Undo is followed by the name of the tool you are using.  For
example, the Undo Line menu item appears when you select the Line tool.
  

