<p>
To copy an image for use in another window:
<list>(numbered)
<le>Use the Box or the Scissors to select the image.
<le>Choose Copy for the Edit menu.
<p>
Paint copies the image to the clipboard.

<le>Choose Paste from the Edit menu to paste the image onto the canvas.
