<head3>(Style\text_style)
<p>
The Style menu item allows you to choose among three text styles.
<p>
To choose your text style:
<list>(numbered)
<le>Pull down the Text menu and drag to the arrow in 
the Style menu item.  A submenu appears.  A shaded check button marks the 
current text style.
<le>Drag to the text style you want:  Normal, Italic, or Bold.
<le>Release MB1.
<p>
The text style is set.  The shaded check button now precedes your choice 
on the Style submenu.
<endlist>

<P>
