<head3>(Line Width...\options_line_width)
<p>
The Line Width... menu item allows you to change the shape of the current 
line.
<p>
Lines drawn with the shape tools can be thick or thin.  To
change the current line width:

<list>(numbered)
<le>Choose Line Width... from the Options menu.
<p>
The Line Width dialog box appears.
<le>Click on the line thickness you want.
<le>Click on OK.  
<endlist>


