<head3>(Patterns...\options_patterns)
<p>
The Patterns... menu item allows you to choose an outline and fill 
pattern.
<p>
To change the outline and fill pattern,
choose Patterns... from the Options menu.  The Patterns dialog box 
appears.
<p>
The Patterns dialog box lets you choose from a selection of 
designs.
<p>
To choose an outline pattern and fill pattern:
<list>(numbered)
<le>Click on the Outline Pattern radio button.  Choose the outline pattern 
by clicking on one of the following:
<list>(unnumbered\-)
<le>The solid box to specify a solid color
<le>The empty box to specify the absence of an outline pattern
<le>One of the patterned boxes from the palette
<endlist>
<p>The outline pattern you select appears in the Outline Pattern check 
button.
<le>Click on the Fill Pattern radio button.  Choose the fill pattern in the 
same manner as you chose the outline pattern.
<p>The fill pattern you select appears in the Fill Pattern check button.
<le>Click on OK.
<endlist>


<P>
