<head3>(Grid On/Off\options_grid)
<p>
The Grid On menu item allows you to choose the grid option.
<p>
To line up a series of shapes or draw them equidistant to each
other, choose Grid On from the Options menu.  A
horizontal and vertical pattern of dots is superimposed
on the drawing window.  
<p>
When you choose Grid On, the menu item toggles to read
Grid Off.  
<p>
To turn off the grid option, choose Grid Off from the Options menu.  

<P>
