<p>
If you want to specify your own
percentages, enter a number less than 100 to shrink the figure or a number
greater than 100 to expand the figure.
 
<le>Click on OK.
<endlist>
<p>
To reverse the process and return to the original picture, choose Undo
Scale from the Edit menu.
<p>
To scale the entire
canvas, choose Scale Picture... from the Edit menu.
You cannot undo this operation.
  
<P>
