<head2>(Using the Scale Picture Dialog Box\scale_picture_dbox)
<p>
When you choose Scale Picture... from the Edit menu, the Scale Picture
dialog box appears.
<note>
You cannot undo the scaling operation.
<endnote>
<p>
To scale your entire picture:

<list>(numbered)
<le>To change the scale for both the x scale and the y scale,
click on one of the percent check buttons for each scale.
<p>
If you want to specify your own
percentages, enter a number less than 100 to shrink the figure or a number
greater than 100 to expand the figure.
 
<le>Click on OK.
<endlist>


<P>
